dct_title_s: Y.W.C.A. war work centers in the United States
dct_description_sm: prepared by C.S. Hammond & Company, Inc.
Inset map of New York City area.

Shows hostess houses (white or colored) in operation, hostess houses (white or colored) authorized and under construction, girls' clubs, emergency housing for girls, and locations with International Institutes for Young Women and Y.W.C.A. city associations.
